Overview

This dashboard shows DNS Security overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested DNS Security logs from Prisma Access.

It showcases the top actions executed by the firewall, the leading DNS resolver IP addresses, response codes, source IPs, and users. Additionally, it provides insights into DNS Security events categorized by record type.
